quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,"Gom…óii malaama gom…óin…ďe Alla golliroo…ďe sari'a Makko …ďen sabu hi…ďugol ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe …óa…ď…ďaynoo kon, e da…óugol ko …ďe hulunoo kon."
  23,2,"∆Āen ko…ďe e nder Julde ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe hoykinii…ďe, hara terde ma…ď…ďe …óen no dee∆īi e nder mayre, …ďer…óe ma…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen no yeewi immorde e soklaaji."
  23,3,"E …ďen …óurnii…ďe e meere nden e puyndan …óan e kala ko goopi immorde e kongu…ói …óin maa…óum kuu…óe …óen."
  23,4,"E …ďen gollay…ďe fii la…ď…ďinngol wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin immorde jikkuuji bon…ói, e la…ď…ďinirgol jawle ma…ď…ďe …óen yaltinngol Jakka majje."
  23,5,"E …ďen …ďe ka√Īun ko reenir…ďe farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin wo…ó…óintingol …ói e jeeno(jina) e luutiyaagu e bonkiiji …óin, kam…ďe ko …ďe nefoo…ďe ko boni laa…ďu…ďe."
  23,6,"Si wanaa e sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe maa…óum ko …ďe mari kon immorde e hor…ďe, haray kam…ďe …ďe feletaake fii dakmitorgol…ďe mbalndi e tanaa mu'un."
  23,7,"Kala …óa…ď…ďu…óo dakmitorgol ko wonaa sonnaa…ďe makko …ďen maa…óum hor…ďe makko …ďe o jeyi …ďen, haray kanko ko o yawtu…óo keeri Alla …óin sabu yawtugol ko O dagini kon dakmitorgol yaha e ko O harmini kon e mu'un."
  23,8,"E …ďen …ďe ka√Īun ko…ďe reenu…ďe ko Alla halfini …ďe kon, maa…óum ko jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen halfini …ďe kon, e aadiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďe yeebataako …ói, ko woni hi…ďe humna …ói."
  23,9,"E …ďen …ďe ka√Īun ko…ďe reenir…ďe Jul…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen duumagol e majje, e tottugol …óe e nder waqtuuji majje e wonndude e ruknuuji majje e wa…ó…óii…ói majje e yi…óaa…ói majje."
  23,10,"∆Āee sifor…ďe …óii sifaaji …óoo ko kam…ďe woni ronoo…ďe …ďen."
  23,11,"∆Āen …ďe no ronoya Aljanna …ďur…óo toowude on kam…ďe ko …ďe √Īii…ďay…ďe e nder makko poomaa, neemaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin ta∆īataa nder ton."
  23,12,"Gom…óii Men tagii baaba …ďanndinke on Aadama immorde e loopal, ∆īettaama mbullaare mu'un immorde e tamannde yaltinaande e ndiyam jillondir…óam e mbullaari leydi ndin."
  23,13,"Refti Men tagi ge…óal…ďe(genyol) makko …ďen ko …ďe jibinay…ďe immorde e to…ď…ďere [maniiyu] nde no √Īii…ďa ka rennga haa fewndo jibinngol ngol."
  23,14,"Men Tagi …ďaawo …óum to…ď…ďere √Īii…ďunde nden ka rannga he…ó…óere wo…óeere, refti Men wa…ói nden to…ď…ďere wo…óeere wano huyre teewu ∆īakkande, Men Tagi huyre nden ∆īi'e sa…ótu…óe, Men …ďorni …óen ∆īi'e teewu, refti Men fu…ó…ói mo Tagu goo sabu wuttugol ruuhu on e makko, e yaltinngol mo faade e ngurndan, Barkii Alla Mo∆ī∆īo Tagu…óo."
  23,15,"Refti onon yim…ďe …ďen, …ďaawo kon ko wuli…óon wuli…óon(bennudon) e mu'un immorde e …óin …ďor…ói(jolde) aray maayon tuma huu…ďugol laje moo…óon."
  23,16,"Refti pellet, onon …ďaawo maayugol moo…óon ko on imminoytee…ďe ka genaale mo'on √Ďalnde Darngal; fii yo on hasbe e dow kon ko ardinno…óon immorde e golle."
  23,17,"Gom…óii Men Tagii dow moo…óon -onon yim…ďe …ďen- kammuuli jee…ói…ói yoga e majji no dow yoga, Men laataaki welsindii…ďe fii tagu Amen ngun, Men wonaali kadi yejjitu…ďe ngu."